description: This Skill will guide you through a Pilates sequence of exercises. If you are familiar with Pilates it will be a joy to have Alexa teach you a Pilates class. The class is a Basic Beginner Pilates Class and it lasts about 20-30 minutes long. All you need for this class is a Pilates mat and the wiliness to feel great! To learn more about Pilates exercies and take a variety of Pilates class including video classes, visit ALotOfPilates.com
exampleInteractions: Alexa, start pilates class and go
Alexa, start pilates class and begin
name: ALOP-Pilates-Class-Skill
shortDescription: Take a pilates class from ALotOfPilates.com. Get ready to feel great!
